reviewText: another great music dvd not seen in music stores here in new zealand,,being a avid fan & collecter ov anything iron maiden, when i saw that the GIRL GROUP had done a release, just had to hav,,,good on you AMAZON

Awesome DVD! This is what you get if you're an Iron Maiden fan and love female fronted metal bands...The Iron Maidens! This is the only available DVD of this great tribute band and only available in Japan. Disc 1 is the full 2010 concert in Japan of 18 tracks. Disc 2 is the special features of great stuff of the band. Great show...Great tribute band...up the ironettes!!!
Kick ass! This tribute band for iron maiden is freakin spot on man! These chicks rock period! You like maiden you will love this dvd!
